A collection of image processing scripts used (mostly) for the Hesperian Wiki.

tawnia/ Scripts for Tawnia
	convert_image.sh - converts .png images in a source directory to transparent background images in a dest directory.

image_convert.pl - front end for various imageMagik convert commands
		transparent - make a grey on white image grey on transparent 
		resize - normalize the image size to shrink high-res images
